snippet.title: Best VGM 823 - Sonic Colors - Planet Wisp Map
snippet.description:
See also:
Best VGM 926 - http://www.youtube.com/watch?v=1gZaH16gqgk

A collection of my favorite videogame music. Note that most of them are from games I played so I might miss some great ones from games I never played.

Nintendo Wii
Sonic Colors (2010)
Planet Wisp Map
Kenichi Tokoi, Tomoya Ohtani & Fumie Kumatani
